movie_title: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
title: Darth Maul is no Vader
review: I really missed the presence of a Vader like villain.  Darth Maul doesn't hold a candle to Vader and as a result the film is unbalanced toward the silly side.  The movie is a visual feast, but the story doesn't entertain adults.  Still a must see though.
